## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2a3bf-102"><xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> Umożliwia ustawienie stanu z aplikacji hosta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a3bf-102">The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity> allows for setting the state from the host application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2a3bf-103">Umożliwia to aplikacji hosta zastąpienie bieżącego stanu automatu Stanów.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a3bf-103">This enables the host application to override the current state of a state machine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2a3bf-104">Można to osiągnąć, umieszczenie wystąpienie <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> klasy do WorkflowQueueu o nazwie stałej. <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a3bf-104">This can be accomplished by enqueuing an instance of the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SetStateEventArgs> class to the WorkflowQueue named by the constant <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowActivity.SetStateQueueName?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2a3bf-105">Prostszym sposobem osiągnięcia tego celu jest użycie <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> metody <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> w klasie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a3bf-105">A simpler way to accomplish this is to use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method in the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2a3bf-106">Możesz użyć <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> metody, aby wykonać operację setstate z hosta lub można to zrobić samodzielnie przez umieszczenie zdarzenia do przepływu pracy automatu Stanów, jak pokazano w poniższym przykładzie.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a3bf-106">You can use the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.StateMachineWorkflowInstance.SetState%2A> method to perform a SetState operation from the host, or you can do it yourself by enqueuing an event to the state machine workflow as shown in the following example.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void SetState(string targetStateName)  
{  
      if (targetStateName == null)  
      {  
            throw new ArgumentNullException("targetStateName");  
      }  
      SetStateEventArgs args1 = new SetStateEventArgs(targetStateName);  
      this.WorkflowInstance.EnqueueItemOnIdle("SetStateQueue", args1, null, null);  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2a3bf-107">Przepływ pracy automatu Stanów używa specjalnej kolejki `SetStateQueue` o nazwie do nasłuchiwania tych specjalnych zdarzeń.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2a3bf-107">The state machine workflow uses a special queue called `SetStateQueue` to listen to these special events.</span></span>
